column16: Brandon Crawford flies out to left fielder Mark Canha.
Giants challenged (play at 1st), call on the field was overturned: Hunter Pence singles on a soft ground ball to shortstop Eric Sogard.   Buster Posey to 2nd.
Buster Posey singles on a ground ball to left fielder Mark Canha.
Matt Duffy lines out to shortstop Eric Sogard.
David DeJesus grounds out, second baseman Brett Lawrie to first baseman Mark Canha.
Logan Forsythe singles on a soft line drive to right fielder Josh Reddick.   James Loney to 3rd.

James Loney grounds into a force out, shortstop Marcus Semien to second baseman Brett Lawrie.   Evan Longoria out at 2nd.  James Loney advances to 2nd, on a throwing error by second baseman Brett Lawrie.
Evan Longoria singles on a ground ball to second baseman Brett Lawrie.
Steven Souza Jr.   strikes out swinging.
Jose Altuve flies out to center fielder Billy Burns.
Jonathan Villar singles on a ground ball to right fielder Josh Reddick.
Dustin Pedroia singles on a ground ball to second baseman Eric Sogard.  Jackie Bradley out at 3rd, second baseman Eric Sogard to third baseman Brett Lawrie.
Xander Bogaerts out on a sacrifice bunt, first baseman Mark Canha to second baseman Eric Sogard.   Jackie Bradley to 2nd.
Pablo Sandoval homers (4) on a line drive to right field.
Kyle Seager lines out to center fielder Billy Burns.
Nelson Cruz walks.   Seth Smith to 3rd.    Robinson Cano to 2nd.
Robinson Cano singles on a ground ball to center fielder Billy Burns.   Chris Taylor scores.    Seth Smith to 2nd.
